{
  "stem": "22586.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I went there, you could only speak Yiddish, if you went to their house on holidays, especially when her father was home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have to, had to speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't speak Yiddish too well, so I would go there but not very often on holidays or on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, we observed all the holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We observed strictly, and I-- I would go-- what I remember about holidays, for instance, that on Tish'a B'Av, we used to go to my very religious friends.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to sit there on the floor and pray and-- certain things come back, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We certainly-- because the families were so large-- like, for instance, Passover, over here, the whole family gets together and a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't do that, I guess because we lived in apartments and the apartments were not large enough to accommodate very large families.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for, for Passover, we just had immediate family together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after the dinner, we would go visiting the relatives or they would come to our house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a lot of my father's family, and as well as my mother's family, they lived in, in small towns.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when they came into the city to visit, they would always stay with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nice memories for that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the other hand, on-- in the summers when we were on school vacations, I used to go either to my grandparents-- my father's parents-- for a vacation, or sometime to some of my aunts in Szeredne.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
